about.summary: private member access linting plugin for flake8

name: flake8-self
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "flake8-self" %}
{% set version = "0.2.2" %}
{% set sha256 = "6c592fa16451da6de268ea17cb5878c764797f08c1d5a47a6f886cb0ffc2ccad" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/Korijn/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - flake8

test:
  imports:
    - flake8_self

about:
  home: http://github.com/Korijn/flake8-self
  license: Freely Distributable
  summary: private member access linting plugin for flake8

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Korijn
